            . I was up a setting out a post-chaisethe last witness called out stop thief: I stopped the prisoner, he fell on his knees, and begged for mercy, saying, it would ruin him, and he should strave in goal.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I am took at a nonplus, so that I have nobody here to speak to my character; I have nothing to say.</p>
